query:
SELECT 
  od.ano,
  od.bimestreOperacional,
  od.tipo,
  COUNT(*) as total_videoaulas
FROM videoaulas v
JOIN ofertasDisciplinas od ON v.ofertaDisciplinaId = od.id
WHERE od.ano = 2025
GROUP BY od.ano, od.bimestreOperacional, od.tipo
ORDER BY od.bimestreOperacional;
